
Critical gaps (must-have)
NetBox integration
Connect to NetBox API (not just a placeholder)
CRUD operations for NetBox resources (sites, devices, etc.)
Handle NetBox authentication and API responses
Business rules engine
Order validation logic
Transformation rules (order → NetBox resource mapping)
Workflow/state management for orders
Object enrichment
Add computed/derived fields to NetBox objects
Merge data from multiple sources
Add metadata/tags based on business logic
Virtual object mapping
Abstraction layer over NetBox resources
Virtual resources that don't exist in NetBox
Mapping between virtual and physical NetBox objects
