Focus on demonstrating that you can:
Work with async Rust (tokio) at scale
Design middleware architecture
Implement business logic transformations
Handle real-world API integration challenges
Write maintainable, extensible code
The current MVP shows the foundation; adding these will demonstrate production-ready capabilities.
